data.description: Welcome home to this Beautiful 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom, 3 car garage house with an open floor plan. In the kitchen, enjoy hardwood floors, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, kitchen nook and beautiful maple cabinets. The bedrooms boast huge walk-in closets with a double walk-in master suite with French doors. The master bathroom has a huge walk in shower and whirlpool tub. The beautiful fenced in back yard is sure to become your new sanctuary with great landscaping, outside fireplace and pergolas. Great location! Close to schools, parks and shopping. Schedule your showing today! Open House Sunday, 1-3pm.
